1. *Bebe* imaju veliku potrebu za pažnjom i ljubavlju. (Babies have a great need for attention and love.)

2. *Bebe* su često slatke i smešne. (Babies are often sweet and funny.)

3. Ona je *bebu* često nosila u šetnji. (She often carried the baby for a walk.)

4. *Bebe* se trebaju često maziti i grliti. (Babies need to be cuddled and hugged often.)

5. Ona je *bebu* često igrala sa. (She often played with the baby.)

6. On je svojoj *bebi* često pevao. (He often sang to his baby.)